title: Proposal for a NAOS Finance Syrup Pool and Farm
body:
# PancakeSwap Welcomes NAOS Finance to Syrup Pool!


CAKE holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from NAOS Finance, a DeFi lending protocol that facilitates the borrowing of crypto assets by using real world assets as collateral. 




# The Syrup Pool:
Stake CAKE tokens to earn NAOS tokens!

- **Total Tokens:** 300,000 NAOS 
- **Distribution duration:** 60 days
- **Start block:** 10361600 [**(approx. 9am UTC on August 26th)**](https://www.bscscan.com/block/countdown/10361600)
- **Finish block:** 12089600 [**(approx. 9am UTC on October 25th)**](https://www.bscscan.com/block/countdown/12089600)
- **Token rewards per block:** 0.1736 NAOS


## Max Stake per wallet: 
100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterwards. 

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some juicy pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.


# The Farm:
In order to host the NAOS Syrup Pool, we will need to provide a NAOS-BNB farm that will have 1x CAKE rewards for the first 48 hours and then 0.5x CAKE rewards after that. 


# What is NAOS Finance?
NAOS Finance is a decentralized real world asset (RWA) lending protocol that facilitates the borrowing of crypto native assets by using RWA as collateral. NAOS has established a large network of corporate borrowers and is operating with financing licenses in multiple regions. 
NAOS’ approach to growing the DeFi playing field is to scale RWA on-chain, and to build an all-encompassing ecosystem of innovative fintech solutions. In this ecosystem, NAOS and its partners will co-evolve capabilities around RWA, and push the boundaries for the next generation of DeFi innovations.
NAOS Finance currently has a network of over 2,500 corporate borrowers globally, with over $300M worth of real world assets to be deployed on-chain. Operationally, NAOS is co-developing oracle solutions for RWA with Chainlink and is working with MakerDao on RWA funding.

# How do you stake CAKE to earn NAOS rewards?
If you own CAKE tokens, congratulations! You’re the master of your … pancakes.
Time to step up your taste buds by learning how to stake CAKE with Syrup Pool.
- Visit this webpage: [**https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup** ](https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup )
- Click “Approve CAKE” on the NAOS Syrup Pool 
- Click on the stake button.
- Confirm the transaction.

BEP20 NAOS will also be circulating and transferable on BSC when we start the Syrup pool, so you will be able to harvest your NAOS tokens and trade on PancakeSwap at any time!



# BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

The official NAOS token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is:
[**https://bscscan.com/token/0x758d08864fb6cce3062667225ca10b8f00496cc2**](https://bscscan.com/token/0x758d08864fb6cce3062667225ca10b8f00496cc2)

Any other NAOS token will be a scam and will result in a financial loss for users. Do not buy tokens from any other token address. Always verify the token address before purchasing tokens. If you receive airdrops from another address for NAOS tokens, they will be rotten tokens (but not the cool kind!), and we advise you to ignore them.
